-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--top\"></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-icon__bar header-menu-button-icon__bar--bottom\"></span></span><span class=\"header-menu-button-state\">メニュー</span></button>\n    <nav class=\"header-menu\" id=\"header-menu\">\n      <ul class=\"header-nav\">\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/number\">数字で見るICS</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/message\">社長メッセージ</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/work\">仕事を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/people\">人を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/place\">職場を知る</a></li>\n        <li class=\"header-nav__item\"><a class=\"header-nav__link\" href=\"/recruit/info\">募集要項</a></li>\n      </ul>\n      <p class=\"recruit-header-recruit\"> <a class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\"> <span class=\"recruit-header-recruit-button__text\">ENTRY</span></a></p>\n    </nav>\n  </header><main class=\"recruit-main\">\n\t\n<div class=\"recruit-page-header\">\n<div class=\"container\">\n<h1 class=\"recruit-page-title\" data-english=\"RECRUIT INFO\"><span class=\"recruit-page-title__text\">募集要項</span></h1>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-page-body\">\n<div class=\"recruit-page-bg recruit-page-bg--gradient position-relative mt-60 pb-0\">\n<ul class=\"recruit-info-tab\" id=\"recruit-info-tab\" role=\"tablist\">\n<li class=\"recruit-info-tab__item\" role=\"presentation\"><button class=\"recruit-info-tab-link active\" id=\"recruit-info-new-graduate-tab\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#recruit-info-new-graduate-tab-pane\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"recruit-info-new-graduate-tab-pane\" aria-selected=\"true\">新卒採用</button></li>\n<li class=\"recruit-info-tab__item\" role=\"presentation\"><button class=\"recruit-info-tab-link\" id=\"recruit-info-mid-career\" data-bs-toggle=\"tab\" data-bs-target=\"#recruit-info-mid-career-tab-pane\" type=\"button\" role=\"tab\" aria-controls=\"recruit-info-mid-career-tab-pane\" aria-selected=\"false\">中途採用</button></li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"container\">\n<div class=\"recruit-info-tab-content tab-content\" id=\"recruit-info-tab-content\">\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade show active\" id=\"recruit-info-new-graduate-tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"recruit-info-new-graduate-tab\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<section class=\"recruit-border-section border-top-0 pt-0\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\"><span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">新卒採用を</span>希望される方へ</h2>\n<p class=\"text-center mt-60 mb-0\"><a href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/banner-mynavi-2027.jpg\"  alt=\"マイナビ2027\"></a></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-border-section\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\">求める人物像</h2>\n<div class=\"row justify-content-lg-between gy-5\">\n<div class=\"col-lg-auto\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"border-radius-20 d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/info/img-recruit-info-1.jpg\" srcset=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/img/recruit/info/img-recruit-info-1@2x.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\"></div>\n<div class=\"col-lg-6\">\n<h3 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-white lh-1-8\">仕事を通じて社会の役に立ちたい方</h3>\n<p>仕事を通じて”誰か”のためになってみませんか。</p>\n<p>仕事は、生活の手段という面がありますが、自分を表現できるという面もあります。</p>\n<p>その表現の相手としての”誰か”に思いを巡らす。</p>\n<p>そんな”誰か”を思う気持ちが、行動となる。<br>そしてコミュニケーション・知識・技術、それぞれの成長の糧になる・・・。</p>\n<p>そんな一人一人が集まることで、人々の生活を豊かにしたり、社会課題の解決に繋がる仕事ができると考えます。</p>\n<p class=\"mb-0\">まずは”誰か”のために。</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-border-section\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\">採用の流れ</h2>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow__column recruit-flow__column--3\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-flow-card-header\"><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__step\">STEP1</span><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__text\">マイナビエントリー</span></h3>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card-body\">\n<p>マイナビよりエントリー後、試験予約してください。<br>【試験予約は2026年3月から】</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"d-block mx-auto\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/banner-mynavi-2027.jpg\" alt=\"マイナビ2027\"><a class=\"icon-link-blue mt-3\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">マイナビページへ</a></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow__column recruit-flow__column--3\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-flow-card-header\"><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__step\">STEP2</span><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__text\">応募書類申込み</span></h3>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card-body\">\n<p>一次試験予約後にサンクスメールが届きます。<br>下記の【応募書類】をダウンロードして下さい。応募書類に記入し郵送提出して下さい。</p>\n<h5 class=\"heading-color heading-color--small before-triangle\">応募書類</h5>\n<ol class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li>（1）<a href=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/a01_recruit.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">履歴書</a>（180KB）</li>\n<li>（2）<a href=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/a02_recruit.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">採用応募・個人情報に関する同意書</a>（124KB）</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow__column recruit-flow__column--2\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-flow-card-header\"><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__step\">STEP3</span><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__text\">選考試験</span></h3>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card-body\">\n<p>筆記による適性試験・一般教養試験選考</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow__column recruit-flow__column--2\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-flow-card-header\"><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__step\">STEP4</span><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__text\">二次試験</span></h3>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card-body\">\n<p>グループ面接による選考</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow__column recruit-flow__column--2\">\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-flow-card-header\"><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__step\">STEP5</span><span class=\"recruit-flow-card-header__text\">最終試験</span></h3>\n<div class=\"recruit-flow-card-body\">\n<p>個人面接による選考</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"d-md-flex justify-content-md-between mt-3 small\">\n<p><span class=\"d-block d-md-inline\">採用問い合わせ先：TEL:019-681-2621　</span>（人事グループ直通）</p>\n<p class=\"text-end\">E-mail : <a class=\"text-white\" href=\"mailto:recruit2027@ics.co.jp\">recruit2027@ics.co.jp</a></p>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"recruit-border-section\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\">募集要項</h2>\n<table class=\"table-border-radius\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">募集職種<br class=\"d-none d-md-block\">募集人員</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">システムエンジニア（総合技術職系）　・・・　15名程度<br>総合営業職系／総合事務職系　　・・・　若干名</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">応募方法<br class=\"d-none d-md-block\">（試験予約）</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">※応募書類送付の前にマイナビへのエントリーをお願い致します。<br><p>【2026年3月から試験予約が可能です】<br><a class=\"d-inline-block mt-30\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/banner-mynavi-2027.jpg\" alt=\"マイナビ2027\"></a><br><strong class=\"d-inline-block mt-3\">▼マイナビからエントリーした方へ</strong><br>本画面から以下のファイルをダウンロードして下さい。\n<ol class=\"list-unstyled\">\n<li>（1）<a href=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/a01_recruit.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">履歴書</a>（180KB）</li>\n<li>（2）<a href=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2025/07/a02_recruit.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">採用応募・個人情報に関する同意書</a>（124KB）</li>\n</ol>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">応募資格</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">入社時30歳未満であること<br>大学（大学院含む）及び高専･短大･各種専門校卒（全学部、全学科対象）および卒業見込みであること</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">応募書類提出先</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">株式会社アイシーエス 総務部人事グループ<br>〒020-8544 岩手県盛岡市松尾町17番10号</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">お問い合わせ先</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">TEL:019-681-2621　（人事グループ直通）<br>E-mail : <a href=\"mailto:recruit2027@ics.co.jp\">recruit2027@ics.co.jp</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">初任給</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">大学院卒（修士）234,000円　大卒223,700円<br>短大・高専・専門学校（２年）卒196,700円<br>他手当として（住居手当:27,000円まで・通勤手当:150,000円まで・時間外手当他）\n<div class=\"border-box mt-3\"><strong>★入社1年目 大卒者（例）★</strong><br>初任給223,700円+住居手当27,000円+通勤手当3,800円→ <strong>支給額 254,500円</strong>＋時間外手当</div>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">諸手当</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">管理職手当、役職手当、職務手当、特別職務手当、家族手当、住居手当、通勤手当、地域手当、時間外手当、休日勤務手当、深夜手当、夜間就業手当、割増就業手当</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">勤務時間</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">8:30～17:15（7時間45分勤務）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">休日休暇</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">土曜日・日曜日（完全週休二日制）・祝日・年次有給休暇（初年度より20日付与）・夏季休暇・年末年始休暇・忌引休暇・誕生日休暇・結婚記念日休暇・出産／育児休暇及び休業・介護休業・子の看護休暇等</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">昇給</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">年1回</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">賞与</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">年2回　＋　業績手当（年1回業績による）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">勤務地</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">盛岡市・一関市・秋田市・青森市・仙台市<br>初任地は盛岡市となります</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-white text-center mt-60\"><span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">皆さんのご応募</span>お待ちしております！</h2>\n<p class=\"text-center mb-0 maw-620 mx-auto\"><a class=\"arrow-button\" href=\"https://job.mynavi.jp/27/pc/search/corp63373/outline.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">エントリーはこちら</a></p>\n</section>\n</div>\n<div class=\"tab-pane fade\" id=\"recruit-info-mid-career-tab-pane\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"recruit-info-mid-career\" tabindex=\"0\">\n<section>\n<div class=\"recruit-border-section border-top-0 pt-0\">\n<h2 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading mb-0\"><span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">中途採用を</span>希望される方へ</h2>\n<p class=\"text-center mt-60 mb-0\"><a href=\"https://tenshoku.mynavi.jp/company/232180/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"> <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/2024/07/banner-mynavi-tenshoku.png\"  alt=\"マイナビ転職\"></a></p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-border-section\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\">正社員募集</h3>\n<table class=\"table-border-radius\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">募集職種</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">システムエンジニア</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">職務内容</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">業務システムの設計・開発・保守運用（自治体系、医療系、その他）</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">待遇</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">当社規定による<br>　勤務地／岩手県盛岡市 予定<br>　勤務時間／8:30～17:15<br>　休日休暇／完全週休二日（土日）<br>　　　　　　祝日・年次・年末年始・夏季・慶弔等々</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\">その他</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">【U・Iターン歓迎】◎業務システム開発やWebアプリケーション開発経験がある方（年数不問）<br>※Java　C#　VB.NET などのスキルのある方は尚可！</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-border-section\">\n<h3 class=\"recruit-border-section-heading\">応募方法</h3>\n<p class=\"text-center\">本社総務部人事グループへ電話連絡の上、履歴書および職務経歴書をご郵送ください<br>　※書類到着次第 随時選考試験実施予定</p>\n<table class=\"table-border-radius mt-40\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th class=\"text-center\" scope=\"row\" style=\"width: 20%;\">書類送付先 <br class=\"d-none d-md-block\">問合せ先</th>\n<td style=\"width: 80%;\">〒020-8544<br>岩手県盛岡市松尾町17番10号<br>株式会社アイシーエス<br>管理本部　総務部　人事グループ　TEL：019-681-2621 （人事グループ直通）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h3 class=\"heading-color heading-color--large text-white text-center mt-60 mb-0\"><span class=\"d-block d-lg-inline\">皆さんのご応募</span>お待ちしております！</h3>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"recruit-page-footer\">\n<div class=\"container\"><nav role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"現在位置\"><ol class=\"breadcrumb\"><li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"/\">ホーム</a></li>  <li class=\"breadcrumb-item\"><a href=\"/recruit\">採用サイトトップ</a></li>  <li class=\"breadcrumb-item active\" aria-current=\"page\">募集要項</li></ol></nav></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</main>\n\n        <footer class=\"recruit-footer\">\n                            <h2 class=\"recruit-footer-entry-heading\">募集要項</h2>\n                <ul class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list\">\n                    <li class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list__item\"><a class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link\" href=\"/recruit/info\"> <span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__text\">新卒採用</span><span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__arrow\"></span></a></li>\n                    <li class=\"recruit-footer-entry-list__item\"><a class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link\" href=\"/recruit/info?tab-id=recruit-info-tab&tab-target-id=recruit-info-mid-career-tab-pane\"> <span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__text\">中途採用</span><span class=\"recruit-footer-entry-link__arrow\"></span></a></li>\n                </ul>\n                        <div class=\"recruit-footer-bottom\"> \n                <p class=\"recruit-footer-bottom-logo\"> <img src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom//assets/img/recruit/common/logo-recruit-footer.svg\" alt=\"アイシーエス　採用サイト\"></p>\n                <p class=\"recruit-footer-bottom-copyright\">© ICS Co., Ltd. All Rights Reserved.</p>\n            </div>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n    <script type=\"speculationrules\">\n{\"prefetch\":[{\"source\":\"document\",\"where\":{\"and\":[{\"href_matches\":\"/*\"},{\"not\":{\"href_matches\":[\"/ics_cms/wp-*.php\",\"/ics_cms/wp-admin/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/uploads/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/plugins/*\",\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/*\",\"/*\\\\?(.+)\"]}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\"a[rel~=\\\"nofollow\\\"]\"}},{\"not\":{\"selector_matches\":\".no-prefetch, .no-prefetch a\"}}]},\"eagerness\":\"conservative\"}]}\n</script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/js/libs/bootstrap.bundle.min.js\" id=\"site-bootstrap-js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/themes/custom/assets/js/common.js\" id=\"site-common-js\"></script>\n<script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"/ics_cms/assets/plugins/page-links-to/dist/new-tab.js\" id=\"page-links-to-js\"></script>\n  </body>\n</html>\n","finalUrl":"https://www.ics.co.jp/recruit/info","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-24T00:02:11.072Z"}